Tell HN: Cloudflare Enabling Theft of Small Business's Website
text:
A contact of mine Melanie, owner of "Tragic Beautiful", a small business in Australia, is desperately seeking help as a Chinese company has stolen her entire website, and Cloudflare is enabling the theft to continue.

The scam company purchased the domain www.tragicbeautyus.com and uploaded the stolen site content to scam people, using Melanie's trademarked logo, site pics, and text.

Despite Melanie's efforts, Cloudflare has ignored her for 8 months, even as customers continue to get ripped off and leave bad her reviews.

The site appears to be using Woocommerce and Paypal

Without help from Cloudflare, Melanie's business is vulnerable to significant losses.

If anyone has any ideas on how to stop this theft, or has a contact with Cloudflare, please advise!
